dcterms:description: A dataset used to train and evaluate the AlphaZero algorithm for playing chess, shogi, and Go. The dataset includes self-play games generated by the AlphaZero neural network and is used to improve the algorithm's performance through reinforcement learning.
dcterms:title: AlphaZero Training Dataset
